itemLabel: Maria Stanley, Baroness Stanley of Alderley
itemDescription: English letter writer and liberal advocate

wikipedia_page.main: Maria Stanley, Baroness Stanley of Alderley (born Lady Maria Josepha Holroyd; 1771–1863) was a British letter writer and liberal advocate.

link_mentions.page: Henrietta Stanley, Baroness Stanley of Alderley
response: Henrietta Maria Stanley, Baroness Stanley of Alderley (née Dillon-Lee; 21 December 1807 – 16 February 1895), was a British Canadian-born political hostess and campaigner for the education of women in England.https://archive.org/details/typesofcanadianw01morguoft/page/321
